abstract: >
  A domain-stratified benchmark for LLM metacognitive monitoring.
  1,500 MMLU items, 33 frontier LLMs, 47,151 observations. Type-2
  AUROC per model-domain cell with bootstrap 95% CIs. Companion to
  Cacioli (2026) arXiv preprint.
keywords:
  - large-language-models
  - metacognition
  - confidence-calibration
  - benchmarks
  - psychometrics
